As mentioned before, it will be a character based tokenizer,

3

00:00:09,700  -->  00:00:15,720
which means that it will convert every character in an input string to a separate token.

4

00:00:15,720  -->  00:00:17,600
Before we start working on it,

5

00:00:17,600  -->  00:00:20,500
we need to add some Python touch boiler plate.

6

00:00:20,500  -->  00:00:25,540
First of all, we add Python touch imports that we will use throughout this lesson.

7

00:00:25,540  -->  00:00:28,840
Then we create a device variable which will be

8

