assigned to Cuda if we have GPU available on this machine.

9

00:00:33,200  -->  00:00:39,700
We will use it later to move our tensors and our models to GPU if it is available.

10

00:00:39,700  -->  00:00:42,940
Now, before we start working on the tokenizer itself,

11

00:00:42,940  -->  00:00:45,340
we need to load our dataset.

12

