a long string that will contain all the Shakespeare play.

17

00:01:05,690  -->  00:01:08,950
Now, if we look at the 4,000 characters in the string,

18

00:01:08,950  -->  00:01:12,550
you will see that it contains a part of a Shakespeare play.

19

00:01:12,550  -->  00:01:16,270
This is just the data that we need to train our model.

20

00:01:16,270  -->  00:01:18,650
Now we can start building our tokenizer,

21

00:01:18,650  -->  00:01:22,150
and first, I'll show you the interface that we will implement.

22

00:01:22,150  -->  00:01:25,510
It will have a constructor that receives a vocabulary,

23

00:01:25,510  -->  00:01:28,110
